ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder approving the transfer of Honourable Carole Therrien to the district of Terrebonne
PrecisOrder advising that the HONOURABLE CAROLE THERRIEN, a Judge of the Superior Court of Quebec for the district of Gatineau, be appointed a Judge of the Superior Court of Quebec for the district of Terrebonne, with residence in the territory of Ville de Saint-Jérôme or the immediate vicinity of that territory.
